I have now waded through over 1000 of these messages that have accumulated
over the last couple of days and I think most of us (including myself) miss
the mark about why we use OS/2.

I use OS/2 because I can be more productive and get more work done NOW with
todays applications (DOS/Windows/OS/2) with additional horsepower from 
applications such as DB2/2, etc.  My workstation can be a toy, but OS/2 has
done more to legitimize the Personal Computer than the DOS/Windows combo.

So, all problems, inconsistencies, etc. aside .... OS/2 is the best damn
desktop OS available NOW and TODAY!

